item.description:
1. install dependencies $ yum install -y gcc-c++ pcre pcre-devel zlib zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel  2. make dir $ mkdir /usr/setup $ mkdir /opt/package $ mkdir /usr/setup/nginx $ mkdir /usr/setup/nginx/temp  3. download and upload download tar resource file &lsquo;nginx-1.12.2.tar.gz&rsquo;
upload to &lsquo;/opt/package/&rsquo;
4. intall 4.1 release this tar file $ tar zxf nginx-1.12.2.tar.gz $ cd nginx-1.12.2/  4.2 install $ ./configure --prefix=/usr/setup/nginx --with-http_stub_status_module --with-http_gzip_static_module --with-http_ssl_module --pid-path=/usr/setup/nginx/nginx.pid --lock-path=/usr/setup/nginx/lock/nginx.lock --error-log-path=/usr/setup/nginx/log/error.log --http-log-path=/usr/setup/nginx/log/access.
